<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f5f5f5; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .header { background: #2e7d32; padding: 24px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
    .body { padding: 32px; }
    .body h2 { color: #333333; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 0; }
    .body p { color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .order-id { display: inline-block; background: #f1f8e9; color: #2e7d32; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .5px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px 28px; background: #2e7d32; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
    .footer { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>VNShop</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Đặt hàng thành công! / Order Confirmed!</h2>
      <p>
        Cảm ơn bạn đã đặt hàng tại VNShop.<br/>
        Thank you for your order at VNShop.
      </p>
      {{#if orderId}}
      <p>Mã đơn hàng / Order ID: <span class="order-id">#{{orderId}}</span></p>
      {{/if}}
      <p>{{body}}</p>
      {{#if deepLink}}
      <a class="btn" href="{{deepLink}}">Xem đơn hàng / View Order</a>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        VNShop — Bạn nhận email này vì đã đặt hàng trên VNShop.<br/>
        You received this because you placed an order on VNShop.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
